*** Test Cases ***
Valid login page
    Open Browser to Login page
    Input Username  9950144030
    Input Password  Da@mon20
    Submit Credentials
    Open Electornics
    Open Menu to Samsung
    Open Samsung
    View Option
    Click Moblie
